data.description: Have you dreamed of a gorgeous home with panoramic views where you watch the boats go by and the sun set in the painted sky?! Now it is possible at this price! Located in downtown Crisfield with water views on every level, the home has 3 bedrooms. 2 upper level master bedroom suites have their own private baths.  There is a living room on each level with generous windows to see the magnificent water views and the Crisfield Municipal Park. You truly must see to appreciate. Small additional deeded lot conveys. Wrap around main deck. Upper level front/waterview deck
